These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, romance
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, trike
1. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance | musical    |
| Transport     | airplane    | trike       | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, photographer, chef
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, skiing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the chef is on the left of the videographer##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
4. the photographer is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | chef | videographer | photographer  |
| Sport   | baseball  | skiing  | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, doctor
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, soul, salsa
1. the fan of soul is on the far left or far right##3
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the designer is the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | doctor | designer | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | salsa    | soul        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, woodworking, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
3. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | woodworking | singing |
| Pet     | turtle  | horse    | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, adventure, time-travel
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | animation | time-travel |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | jet-ski   | skateboard   |

