.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, country, blues
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, french, pakistani
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the french##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues    | electronic       |
| Nationality   | french | pakistani | polish |

