.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, tea
There 3 different types of food: banana, pumpkin, cauliflower
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating banana##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea        | juice  | iced-tea   |
| Food       | cauliflower | pumpkin | banana |

 #################################

 
