.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, turkish, thai
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, hamster
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the thai is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goldfish##2
4. the owner of the goldfish is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | chinese | thai | turkish |
| Pet           | pony    | hamster    | goldfish       |

