2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | hiking    | chess   | camping |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | skateboarding | weightlifting |

