.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, satire, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, reggae, pop
1. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is between the fan of pop and the fan of rock##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of pop is the person watching action movies##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | zombie | action |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | reggae  | pop    |

