.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, grapes, pumpkin
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, spy, action
1. the person eating kiwi is the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
3. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
