.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, fantasy, musical
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | milk | cola         |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | fantasy  | action |

 